    {\displaystyle \Pi ^{n}=\left\{{\begin{array}{c}e^{i\phi }A_{1}\otimes \cdots \otimes A_{n}:\forall j\in \left\{1,\ldots ,n\right\}A_{j}\in \Pi ,\ \ \phi \in \left\{0,\pi /2,\pi ,3\pi /2\right\}\end{array}}\right\}.}
  Elements of 
  
    
      
        
          Π
          
